rchase the Hoi An Old Town ticket at any of the <a href=\"#ticket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ticket stalls<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--583x810.jpg\" alt=\"Quan Cong Temple hoi an\"><\/noscript><img width=\"243\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Quan Cong Temple hoi an\" class=\"wp-image-20387 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--583x810.jpg 583w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--300x417.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--600x834.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--432x600.jpg 432w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--243x338.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--1105x1536.jpg 1105w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Cong-Temple-hoi-an--552x768.jpg 552w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122241\/Quan-Co