-attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hoi-an-walking-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Join one of the popular Hoi An Walking Tours (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Join one of the popular Hoi An Walking Tours<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"japanese bridge hoi an\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"japanese bridge hoi an\" class=\"wp-image-20619 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122105\/japanese-bridge-hoi-an-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourh