 and visit the Hoi An Market (Ch&#x1EE3; H&#x1ED9;i An). You can find products like fresh vegetables and fruits, flowers, spices, baskets, and meat and fish. Experiencing the intense crowds, and beeping motorbikes, during the morning is a thing you must do in Hoi An.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/vietnam\/vietnam-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete 3-week Vietnam Route Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-597x810.jpg\" alt=\"market hoi an\"><\/noscript><img width=\"249\" height=\"338\" alt=\"market hoi an\" class=\"wp-image-20395 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-597x810.jpg 597w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-300x407.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-600x814.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-443x600.jpg 443w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122220\/market-hoi-an-249x338.jpg 249w, https:\/\/static.saltino