paring traditional foods, and visiting the outer parts of Hoi An, which you might not usually see. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>The tour is organized every Tuesday, Saturday, and Sunday and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.hoianfreetour.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"can be booked here (opens in a new tab)\">can be booked here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle.jpg\" alt=\"thing to go hoi an bicycle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"thing to go hoi an bicycle\" class=\"wp-image-20527 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122147\/thing-to-go-hoi-an-bicycle-450x338.jpg 450w