 vegetables and herbs on their farm and how to cook traditional Vietnamese meals. Cycle amongst the rice fields and paddle in a tiny basket boat. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cooking-class-hoian-farm\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read reviews &amp; book here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-class.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do hoi an cooking class\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best things to do hoi an cooking class\" class=\"wp-image-20297 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-class.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-class-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-class-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-class-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122304\/best-things-to-do-hoi-an-cooking-cla