s of Vietnam.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hoi-an-all-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">These are all hotels to stay in Hoi An<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-595x810.jpg\" alt=\"art gallery hoi an\"><\/noscript><img width=\"248\" height=\"338\" alt=\"art gallery hoi an\" class=\"wp-image-20391 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 595px) 100vw, 595px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-595x810.jpg 595w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-300x409.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-600x817.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-441x600.jpg 441w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-248x338.jpg 248w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-1128x1536.jpg 1128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122233\/art-gallery-hoi-an-22x30.j