x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-163x125.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-234x180.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-768x590.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-1024x786.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-1407x1080.jpg 1407w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-1876x1440.jpg 1876w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23122022\/vietnam.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"restaurants\">Restaurants in Hoi An<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hoi An is a place for food lovers with well-established local and international cuisines. These are our favorites:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>N&#xFA; eatery&#xA0;(Fusion Vietnamese)<\/li><li>Nourish eatery (International, Vegan)<\/li><li>Streets Restaurant (International) <\/li><li>Vegetarian Ban Mi&#xA0;(Vietnamese)<\/li><li>Avo&#x2019;s and Mango (International) <\/li><li>Qu&#xE1;n Cao l&#x1EA7;u B&#xE1; L&#x1EC5; (Vietnamese)<\/li><li>Nhan&#x2019;s Kitchen (Vietnamese)<\/li><li>The Espresso Station (Best coffee)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default i