ach or situate yourself more centrally by the old town. It&#x2019;s best to stay just outside of the old town, as the accommodation will be cheaper and both the beach and the old town will still be easy to reach.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hoi-an-all-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">These are all hotels to stay in Hoi An<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hoi-an-acacia-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121942\/123019934-30x20.jpg\" alt=\"Acacia Heritage Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121942\/123019934-450x300.jpg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Acacia Heritage Hotel<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n 